          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说那一黑汉子，你在酒席筵前，将我的纱帽，打在尘埃，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难道你不认识某家么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不过也是朝中一个臣子，与我一般，何足为奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大马兰，你官居何职？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我妹子，乃是西宫国母，陪王伴驾，我是当朝国舅，谁人不知，哪个不晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我弟兄，东荡西除，南征北剿，才得封为王位，你不过是裙带脂粉官儿，真\n真好不知羞耻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。你欺压大臣，是何理也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满口胡言，招打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马兰下。三朝官同劝，李刚下，三朝官同下。）"
        }
      ],
