    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "内侍",
        "是与不是上金殿",
        "李广",
        "皇上",
        "莫不是烟尘又起反",
        "马兰",
        "马妃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马妃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙凤阁内换新妆，朝朝暮暮伴君王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马兰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可恨李刚太欺情，\n去到宫中说分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马兰参见娘娘千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长少礼请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长进宫何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再不要提起。只因今日，万岁与李广庆功，命我陪宴。可恨李刚倚仗兄长声威，\n不问青红皂白，将愚兄骂了一顿，反道娘娘，好比前朝褒姒妲己一般，真真\n可恼。望求娘娘作主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长请回，我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢娘娘。\n正是：李广呀，李广，管叫你明枪容易躲，暗箭最难防。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马兰下。四太监、皇上上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "朝罢了文武臣转回宫，\n往见了我爱梓童细说端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日朝中，不知有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并无军情，惟有李广弟兄，征战虹霓有功，分功论赏，大宴群臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏万岁：李广弟兄，在朝专权，大有谋反之意，如若不及早灭却，日后只恐\n万岁江山难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事你是怎生知晓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我兄长马兰，方才言讲，李刚在酒席筵前，亲自讲的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来心头恨，\n大骂李广乱胡行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马妃暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "快宣李广上龙庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内侍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣亚父李广上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李广上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "乌鸦不住叫连天，\n叫得李广心胆寒。\n弟兄征剿方才还。\n参王驾来问王安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫不是烟尘又起反、是与不是上金殿、皇上",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见李广怒冲冠，\n大骂卖国狗奸馋。\n要夺小王锦江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四刀斧手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将他人头挂高竿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忠臣无故反遭斩，\n身受惨刑为哪般。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四刀斧手押李广同下。马兰上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "迈步撩袍上金殿，\n马兰要讨监斩官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马兰见驾，吾皇万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家上殿，有何本奏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁斩首李广，不知命何人监斩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就命你监斩。午时三刻，斩头交旨。\n内侍退班。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（皇上下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金殿领圣命，法场斩仇人。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
