    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四龙套",
        "李广",
        "马兰"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李广 （内西皮导板） 忠良被害气冲牛斗，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李广上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由人一阵阵珠泪交流。\n我弟兄保太子逃出龙楼。\n在北门身中箭一命罢休。\n再不能领人马共统貔貅。\n再不能在朝房同把——"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "本奏，\n再不能在金殿共定机谋；\n再不能到夏来避暑在高楼；\n再不能到冬来教子攻读春秋。\n这就是忠良臣下场头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。四龙套、马兰同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时辰可到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时辰未到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管他到与不到，推去斩了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套推李广同下，斩，同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李广斩讫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马兰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上殿交旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马兰、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
