      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、皇上同上。内侍上，报。皇上跑，闭宫。李刚、李虎同上，同打门。土地上，持杖挡。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昏王呀，昏王！想我弟兄在朝，东荡西除，南征北剿，有十大汗马功劳，你不\n该听信马兰兄妹谗言，将我兄长杀死，你是何道理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启王爷：天色已晚，明日再与昏王辩理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日天色已晚，明日再与你辩理。昏王，你要与我仔细了，你要与我打定了。\n我那兄长呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李刚、李虎同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇上",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见李刚出宫门，\n吓得小王心内惊。\n见了国太定计行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
